Exception Handling:-
It is a mechanism to handle runtime errors such as classNotFoundException, IOException, SQLException etc.

Error Types:
1.Assertion
2.Exception

Exception Types:-
1.Compiletime(Checked exception)
2.Runtime(unchecked exception)

Runtime exception class:-
1.Predefined:-

Common Senerio of Java Exception:-

1.ArithmeticException:
ex. int a =50/0;

2.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundException:-
int a[] = newint[5];
a[10] = 50;
    
3.NullPointerException:-
ex. String s = null;
    System.out.println(s.length());
    
4.NumberFormatException:-
String s = "abc";
int = Integer.parseInt(s);

etc..
